Auth (features/auth/)
Fully implemented:

AuthProvider stores accessToken + user in localStorage
useAuth() exposes user, isAuthenticated, login(), logout()
ProtectedRoute redirects to /login if unauthenticated
AuthForm handles both login and register (single shared component, mode prop)
Token refresh interceptor in lib/api.ts — on 401, retries with refresh cookie, then redirects to /login
